<h1>BBC News My City - category travel</h1>

<p>See the world's greatest cities through the eyes of BBC World Service reporters who lived there:  <a href="http://www.bbc.com/travel/mycity">My City series</a> opens a door to what life is really like in their home city.</p> 
 
<p>From <a href="http://www.bbc.com/travel/video/my-city/20121203-ho-chi-minh-city">Ho Chi Minh's scooter club</a> to <a href="http://www.bbc.com/travel/video/my-city/20130625-my-city-accra">the boxing suburb of Bukom in Accra</a>, the films convey the vivid sights and sounds of each place.</p>
 
<p>As well as being published on <a href="http://www.bbc.com/travel">www.bbc.com/travel</a> and shown on <strong>BBC World TV</strong>, the series was translated into several different languages and published on BBC's World Service websites.</p>

